data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the west of Lake Worth! This fully renovated single-family house boasts a new roof and AC installed in 2022, ensuring modern comfort. With hurricane shutters, water filter & softener in entire house, custom closets, and porcelain floors throughout, it exudes both style and practicality. The quartzite countertops in the open-concept kitchen add a touch of luxury. Featuring a convenient split floor plan, the 3 bedrooms and 2 baths provide ample space. The entertainment room, convertible into a 4th bedroom, offers versatility. Step outside to your private pool in a fenced yard, creating a perfect oasis. The two-car garage with separate AC unit ensures convenience, and with very low HOA and no restrictions, you have the freedom to make it truly your own..... Located just 10 minutes from I-95 and the Turnpike, and within walking distance to an elementary school, it's a blend of accessibility and community. Proximity to parks, malls, shopping centers, banks, and supermarkets makes this home a hub of convenience and comfort. Welcome to the embodiment of modern living!
